comment: Permutation of the positive integers, inverse: A258226.
link: Reinhard Zumkeller, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..9999
Index entries for sequences that are permutations of the natural numbers
program: (PARI) lista(nn) = {v = []; vs = vecsort(v); for (n=1, nn, k=3; pt = 10^(#digits(n)); while (! (((k % pt) == n) && !vecsearch(vs, k)), k+=3); v = concat(v, k); vs = vecsort(v); print1(k/3, ", "););} \\ _Michel Marcus_, Jun 26 2015
